# Optional: a GitHub personal access token (classic or fine-grained, no scopes needed
# for public data). Raises the API rate limit from 60 to 5000 requests/hour.
# The token is only ever read on the server — it is never shipped to the browser.
GITHUB_TOKEN=

# Optional: override the GitHub API base URL (used to point the proxy at a
# mock server in tests). Leave unset in normal use.
# GITHUB_API_URL=https://api.github.com
